data.description: Beautiful open floor plan with spacious updated kitchen and appliances. Split floor plan, 3 bedroom 2 bath. Gas fireplace in spacious living area opens to tropical fenced back living area with Koi pond. Mature landscape on automatic drip system, storage shed, RV hookups with 50 amp power on side of garage. Security system, new roof in 2022 and room for RV parking or plenty of room on this 1 acre to build a shop or RV  garage.  Large 3 car garage, paved city street and many more amenities to enjoy.AGENTS-SEE REALTOR ONLY COMMENTS(3rd Bedroom being used as den)
